text: RTV Visoko or Televizija Visoko is a local Bosnian public television channel based in Visoko municipality. Under this name, it was established in 1994 when local Radio Visoko started television broadcasting. RTV Visoko broadcasts a variety of programs such as local news, local sports, mosaic and documentaries. Program is mainly produced in Bosnian language. Radio Visoko is also part of public municipality services. == References == == External links == * Official website of RTV Visoko * Communications Regulatory Agency of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Television channels and stations established in 1994 Category:Television stations in Bosnia and Herzegovina
